52\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.52</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n70105.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ υἱός μου ν. ἦν καὶ ἀνέζησε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0031.tlg003.perseus-grc1:15:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Ev.Luc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.24</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄνομα ἔχεις ὅτι ζῇς καὶ ν. εἶ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0031.tlg027.perseus-grc1:3:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Apoc.\">Apoc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.1</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ν. τῇ ἁμαρτίᾳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0031.tlg006.perseus-grc1:6:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Ep.Rom.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.11</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n70105.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in pl., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the dead,</tr_> as dwellers in the nether world, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κλυτὰ ἔθνεα νεκρῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:526\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.526</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.34</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐν νεκροῖς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg027:87(